    "rating": 5,
    "when": "a month ago",
    "publishTime": "a month ago",
    "text": "I cannot thank Nick enough for the incredible service.\nMy van broke down near Heathrow, which is one of the worst places to be stranded, and I was honestly very stressed. I called Nick and from the first minute he was calm, professional and reassuring. He told me he would arrive within 45 minutes — and he did exactly that..\nHe gave me a very fair price upfront over the phone, with complete transparency. No hidden costs, no last-minute surprises.\nMy Ford Transit Custom is a heavy van, but his 7-ton recovery truck handled it perfectly. You could immediately see he has the right equipment and real experience with larger vehicles.\nHe turned a very stressful situation into a smooth and professional experience. Reliable, honest and genuinely helpful.\nI highly recommend Nick to anyone who needs recovery, especially around Heathrow. 10/10 service."
  },
